headline: This Could Be the Catalyst That Sends Summit Therapeutics' Stock Higher This Year
summary: Summit Therapeutics (NASDAQ: SMMT) has been one of the hottest stocks to own over the past 12 months, with its valuation soaring 300% during that stretch.  Investors are, after all, paying a hefty premium for a business which still isn't generating any consistent revenue; its market capitalization remains north of $13 billion.  Hype and excitement around the potential for Summit's cancer treatment candidate, ivonescimab, has fueled the stock's rally.
